OL,3,CWatchdog urges ministers to do more to
OL,4,Clower 'world-beatingly high' energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe government should improve its
OL,8,Fresponse to future energy price spikes
OL,9,Fas Britons face "world-beatingly high"
OL,10,Fbills, Parliament's spending watchdog
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FElectricity bills in 2023 were the
OL,14,Fhighest among 25 comparable countries,
OL,15,Fwith consumers owing #3.7 billion for
OL,16,Fgas and electricity in 2024, more than
OL,17,Fdouble the amount in 2021, a report by
OL,18,Fthe Public Accounts Committee (PAC)
OL,19,Fsaid.
