OL,3,CWatchdog urges ministers to do more to
OL,4,Clower 'world-beatingly high' energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe committee urged the Department for
OL,8,FEnergy Security and Net Zero (DESNZ)
OL,9,Fto improve support for households
OL,10,Fvulnerable to fuel poverty and create
OL,11,Fa clear plan and timeline for policy
OL,12,Fdecisions to make bills cheaper.
OL,14,FChairman of the committee Sir Geoffrey
OL,15,FClifton-Brown said: "Sharp moves in
OL,16,Fenergy prices in the future must find
OL,17,FGovernment fully prepared to issue
OL,18,Ftargeted and effective support, with
OL,19,Fthose most in need the focus of that
OL,20,Fsupport.
