OL,7,F"We cannot see a repetition of
OL,8,Fprecious funds being beamed out across
OL,9,Fthe spectrum to those who do not
OL,10,Frequire help.
OL,12,F"This approach is all the more
OL,13,Fimportant when our report shows some
OL,14,Fhouseholds remain exposed, at a time
OL,15,Fwhen the UK's electricity bills appear
OL,16,Fworld-beatingly high and debt weighs
OL,17,Fdown bill-payers' finances to an
OL,18,Falarming degree."
