OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FIt said the department and regulator
OL,8,FOfgem "are not doing enough" to ensure
OL,9,Fpeople falling into debt with their
OL,10,Fenergy bills receive proper advice and
OL,11,Fsupport and urged them to develop more
OL,12,Ffinancial support for next winter.
OL,14,F"We remain concerned that even after
OL,15,Fthe crisis has subsided, UK
OL,16,Felectricity bills are the highest of
OL,17,Fthe countries providing comparable
OL,18,Fdata to the International Energy
OL,19,FAssociation," the report reads.
