OL,3,CWatchdog urges ministers to do more to
OL,4,Clower 'world-beatingly high' energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,F"The UK had the highest electricity
OL,8,Fprice out of 25 countries reporting
OL,9,Fboth domestic and industrial
OL,10,Felectricity prices in 2023, (including
OL,11,Ftaxes and levies) and electricity is
OL,12,Fcurrently four-times more expensive
OL,13,Fthan gas.
OL,15,F"Despite repeated promises, the
OL,16,Fdepartment has delayed taking action
OL,17,Fto rebalance energy prices by shifting
OL,18,Fthe cost of environmental levies from
OL,19,Felectricity to gas."
