OL,7,FThe report said that while the DESNZ
OL,8,Fis reviewing how electricity prices
OL,9,Fare set for households so that they
OL,10,Fcan benefit from cheaper rates if
OL,11,Fdemand is low or when the weather
OL,12,Fmeans more energy is produced, the
OL,13,Freview has been "running for three
OL,14,Fyears and remains on an uncertain
OL,15,Ftimetable".
OL,17,FThe committee said ministers must do
OL,18,Fmore to convince Parliament that it
OL,19,Fhas a "robust plan" for ensuring
OL,20,Fsecurity of energy supply amid
OL,21,Fincreasing global tensions.
