OL,7,F"Switching or fixing tariffs now,
OL,8,Fwhere possible, could also help
OL,9,Fconsumers to bring costs down.
OL,11,F"We've introduced tougher rules to
OL,12,Fmake sure energy companies do more to
OL,13,Fspot the signs when a customer may be
OL,14,Fstruggling and step in to offer
OL,15,Fsupport, including working out
OL,16,Faffordable payment plans and providing
OL,17,Femergency credit to reduce the risk of
OL,18,Fself-disconnection.
