OL,7,F"We have also made pre-payment meters
OL,8,Fthe cheapest way to pay for energy,
OL,9,Fand are consulting on plans to
OL,10,Fintroduce a scheme that could provide
OL,11,Fdirect support to those struggling
OL,12,Fwith unmanageable levels of debt.
OL,14,F"We continually monitor the service
OL,15,Fsuppliers are providing to their
OL,16,Fcustomers and where they are falling
OL,17,Fshort, we hold them to account.
OL,18,FHowever, the issue of debt is one that
OL,19,Frequires action from everyone across
OL,20,Fthe sector and government."
