OL,7,FA Department for Energy Security and
OL,8,FNet Zero spokesperson said: "Our
OL,9,Fmission for clean power is the only
OL,10,Fway to protect UK billpayers from
OL,11,Ffuture price shocks.
OL,13,F"The 2022-23 energy crisis, which saw
OL,14,Fsky-high energy bills and put pressure
OL,15,Fon households and businesses across
OL,16,Fthe country, was a product of our
OL,17,Freliance on gas for heating and
OL,18,Fpowering our homes.
