OL,7,F"We will bring down bills for good by
OL,8,Fmoving towards a clean, homegrown
OL,9,Fpower system that we control.
OL,11,F"We are also rolling out support for
OL,12,Fconsumers, including through proposals
OL,13,Fto expand the Warm Home Discount to
OL,14,Falmost three million more households
OL,15,Fnext winter, and allocating #1.8
OL,16,Fbillion of funding to create warmer,
OL,17,Fmore energy-efficient homes across
OL,18,FEngland."
